              asperiores numquam quod.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div
            class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row justify-center items-center py-3"
          >
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-medium text-2xl md:text-3xl pb-2 xl:text-4xl">
                Our Strategy
              </h3>
              <p class="text-neutral-500 font-normal xl:text-base">
                Lorem ipsum, dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. At,
                inventore.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3
                class="font-medium text-2xl md:text-3xl py-2 md:pt-2 xl:text-4xl"
